Verification Plan
1.	Maps: Create a lobby. Ensure typing into the map search auto-centres the map. Verify city/country are extracted and saved.
2.	Feed: Load the feed, click "Near Me". Verify browser asks for location permission and sorts the feed properly.
3.	Chat: Using two accounts (Tab A and Tab B), have User A message User B. Ensure User B receives the real-time notification/message. Verify the UI updates correctly in the /messages generic inbox.
4.	Squads: Navigate to squad profile as captain. Remove a member. Verify roster updates. Verify W/L is gone.
5.	Contact Info: Open any lobby card on the feed and verify the WhatsApp number is legible.
